You keep what you kill!

121
00:17:41.844 --> 00:17:44.806
<i>RIDDICK: Somewhere along the way.
I lost a step.</i>

122
00:17:45.473 --> 00:17:47.267
<i>I got sloppy.</i>

123
00:17:47.850 --> 00:17:49.686
<i>Dulled my own edge.</i>

124
00:17:51.604 --> 00:17:54.691
<i>Maybe I went and did the
worst crime of all...</i>

125
00:17:56.359 --> 00:17:58.444
