132
00:19:27.784 --> 00:19:32.956
<i>Before long. I realized there was
a whole other world over there.</i>

133
00:19:33.915 --> 00:19:36.960
<i>of water. grass and life.</i>

134
00:19:39.170 --> 00:19:42.006
