1032
01:42:20.340 --> 01:42:22.008
(BOTH GRUNTING)

1033
01:42:30.600 --> 01:42:33.061
Thanks for startin' the killing
spree for me. Riddick.

1034
01:42:33.102 --> 01:42:35.021
But I'll take it from here.

1035
