(GRUNTS)
(GROANING)

1041
01:43:27.657 --> 01:43:28.950
Jamoke.

1042
01:43:33.955 --> 01:43:36.833
So that blade you buried
was meant for me?

1043
01:43:38.376 --> 01:43:40.879
Anyone who deserved it. really.

1044
01:43:44.257 --> 01:43:45.633
We've got a problem. Riddick.

1045
01:43:47.552 --> 01:43:50.138
because I've got two nodes here.

1046
01:43:50.179 --> 01:43:52.056
We've got one hog.

1047
01:43:52.223 --> 01:43:56.311
And I sure as shit
am not ridin' bitch with you again.

1048
01:43:58.605 --> 01:43:59.898
One hog?

1049
01:44:01.399 --> 01:44:03.192
You sure about that. Johns?

1050
01:44:09.115 --> 01:44:11.659
He pulled the goddamn turbine pin!

1051
01:44:13.161 --> 01:44:15.205
You just figured that out?

1052
01:44:15.788 --> 01:44:19.250
Diaz was gonna take the nodes
for himself and ghost me.

1053
01:44:19.751 --> 01:44:22.378
He was gonna leave
you out here alone.

1054
01:44:22.921 --> 01:44:24.422
So what now?

1055
01:44:31.804 --> 01:44:34.224
Now we switch to our ground game.

1056
01:44:35.767 --> 01:44:39.062
Let's see if that lack of spine
runs in the family.

1057
