Reload!

1062
01:45:36.828 --> 01:45:38.162
(GRUNTS)

1063
01:45:38.705 --> 01:45:40.373
Watch your head.

1064
01:45:44.627 --> 01:45:46.462
(SHRIEKING)

1065
01:45:47.589 --> 01:45:48.590
