(GRUNTS)

1071
01:46:58.201 --> 01:46:59.536
(GROANING)

1072
01:47:06.543 --> 01:47:07.544
(BEEPS)

1073
01:47:12.257 --> 01:47:13.591
(CREATURES SNARLING)

1074
01:47:33.903 --> 01:47:34.904
(GROANS)

1075
01:47:51.170 --> 01:47:53.798
(GROANING)

1076
01:47:53.923 --> 01:47:55.049
(PINGS)

1077
01:47:55.091 --> 01:47:56.217
I got inbound.

1078
01:48:10.273 --> 01:48:11.274
(GRUNTS)

1079
01:48:11.566 --> 01:48:13.109
Take this!

1080
01:48:13.484 --> 01:48:15.194
Is it just you?

1081
01:48:16.112 --> 01:48:18.448
Just slam this thing in.
See if it's still good. (GRUNTS)

1082
01:48:18.489 --> 01:48:20.575
(GRUNTING)

1083
01:48:21.784 --> 01:48:22.827
Boss...

1084
01:48:22.911 --> 01:48:26.456
Just see if the fucking thing works!
We need to get outta here.

1085
01:48:29.751 --> 01:48:32.295
(GROANING AND PANTING)

1086
01:49:01.908 --> 01:49:02.909
(GROANS IN PAIN)

1087
01:49:09.749 --> 01:49:10.750
(YELLS)

1088
01:49:12.168 --> 01:49:13.503
(GROANING IN PAIN)

1089
01:49:18.508 --> 01:49:20.051
(PANTING)

1090
01:50:01.926 --> 01:50:03.720
(GRUNTING)

1091
01:50:17.191 --> 01:50:18.818
