1103
01:52:20.899 --> 01:52:22.775
(SPACESHIP APPROACHING)

1104
01:52:30.783 --> 01:52:34.245
Extraction. 30 seconds or less.
Let's go. let's go!

1105
01:52:55.266 --> 01:52:56.267
(ROPE ZINGS)

1106
01:53:06.945 --> 01:53:08.738
Let me ask you somethin'.

1107
01:53:09.989 --> 01:53:11.741
sweet-like...

1108
01:53:53.449 --> 01:53:55.285
<i>JOHNS ON RADIO:
Lot of good men died here. Riddick.</i>

1109
01:53:55.743 --> 01:53:59.664
Not sure how I'm supposed to
overlook that. Next time.

1110
01:54:00.039 --> 01:54:02.041
Yeah. Things would
have been different

1111
01:54:02.125 --> 01:54:04.502
if they weren't trying
to put my head in a box.

1112
01:54:07.213 --> 01:54:09.257
So where to now. Riddick?

1113
01:54:09.924 --> 01:54:13.845
You know what? Fuck that. Don't tell me.
I don't wanna know.

1114
01:54:14.679 --> 01:54:16.639
<i>I'll tell you this. Johns.</i>

1115
01:54:17.056 --> 01:54:20.268
<i>Sooner or later.
we all have to head home.</i>

1116
01:54:21.269 --> 01:54:23.479
<i>Tell Dahl to keep
it warm for me.</i>

1117
01:54:24.272 --> 01:54:25.773
And. Johns...

1118
01:54:27.240 --> 01:54:29.140
you keep a strong spine.

